    <item>
      <title>油价上涨、亚洲股市下跌，金价创历史新高：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管亚洲股市周五下跌，但欧洲股指期货上涨。随着中东紧张局势再次升温，金价攀升至新高，油价也恢复上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 22:29:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
